      "content": {
        "fact": "Cursed energy is generated from negative human emotion and is the baseline fuel for jujutsu techniques, curse reinforcement, barriers, and many supernatural effects in Jujutsu Kaisen.",
        "injection": "When a scene uses the JJK power system, treat cursed energy as emotion-derived supernatural fuel. Do not write it as generic mana, science, or harmless aura.",
        "constraints": [
          "Keep the explanation compact unless the scene is explicitly about training or technique mechanics."
        ],
        "antiLore": [
          "Do not let ordinary non-sorcerers understand cursed energy mechanics without a scene-specific reason."
